<div class="entry-category-hair_makeup entry-category-styling entry-author-elsiecake entry-type-post entry" id="entry-6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f8d5970b">
			<h3 class="entry-header">10 Ways To Wear A Silk Scarf</h3>
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<div class="entry-body">
			<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f386970b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="Silk scarf" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f386970b image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f386970b-800wi" title="Silk scarf" /></a><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f3ea970b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="Silk scarf" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f3ea970b image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f3ea970b-800wi" title="Silk scarf" /></a>Hi friend! Today we&#39;re excited to share with you 10 ways to wear one of our favorite staples, silk scarves!</p>
<p>1. Fold your scarf into a long rectangle (you can do this with traditional square scarves or skinny scarves). Tie it behind your head, under your hair.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20163039021ee970d-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="2" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20163039021ee970d image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20163039021ee970d-800wi" title="2" /></a>2. Style your hair into a messy bun or top knot. Fold your scarf into a long rectangle and tie around your head so the knots in the front. Style the knot by twisting or tucking parts of it in.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e2016303902258970d-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="3" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e2016303902258970d image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e2016303902258970d-800wi" title="3" /></a>3. Tie your scarf into a knot in the middle. Style the knot in the front of your head and tie the scarf around your head, over your hair in the back.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98641b2970c-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="4" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98641b2970c image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98641b2970c-800wi" title="4" /></a>4. Style your hair into a pony tail. Tie the scarf over your hair tie so that it looks like a floppy bow!</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20163039023ac970d-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="5" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20163039023ac970d image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20163039023ac970d-800wi" title="5" /></a>5. Tie the scarf onto a strand of your hair in the back. Braid your scarf into your hair and (if long enough) use the end to tie the braid securely.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98642fb970c-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="6" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98642fb970c image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98642fb970c-800wi" title="6" /></a>6. Fold the scarf into a long rectangle and tie around your head, over your hair. This one is super laid-back but cute!</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e986437a970c-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="7" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20168e986437a970c image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e986437a970c-800wi" title="7" /></a>7. Style your hair in a messy bun and tie the scarf around the base of the fun with the knot in the back.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98643e6970c-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="8" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98643e6970c image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e20168e98643e6970c-800wi" title="8" /></a>8. Add color to your outfit by tying your scarf around your neck.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f7c5970b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="9" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f7c5970b image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f7c5970b-800wi" title="9" /></a>9. Fold your scarf into&#0160;a large triangle (this works best with traditional square scarves). Tie the longest two ends around your head and under your hair.</p>
<p><a class="asset-img-link" href="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f815970b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="10" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f815970b image-full" src="http://abeautifulmess.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8358081ff69e201676484f815970b-800wi" title="10" /></a>10. Thinking of wearing your scarf later on? Add a bit contrast to your purse by tying your scarf around one handle in a bow or a cute knot.</p>
<p>By the way, our silk scarves are <a href="http://shopredvelvet.com/collections/accessories" target="_blank">back in stock</a>! Hope you had a wonderful weekend! emma</p>
		</div>
		
		
	</div>
